{"tid":1073203,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿當莊臣獲釋遭禁獨自與女兒相見","createTime":"2019-03-22T13:45:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-22T14:32:17.000Z","uid":153600,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"fe640d89625c5a8587445cd91146208b0cbbe529","tid":1073203,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:45:21.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=WP5iSE3nEMa4dMETfl%2FD1xzw8eMAegQd4vHbNIzLZr4%3D&h=106549f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前英格蘭國腳阿當莊臣出獄後，將不可單獨見其女兒。<br />\n<br />\n前新特蘭球員阿當莊臣（Adam Johnson）性侵犯15歲少女被判入獄，到周五刑滿離開監獄。官員要求他交出電話，如果阿當莊臣在他們不知情的情況下刪除任何東西，可能會再次被監禁。一位消息人士稱：「阿當莊臣將被視為被定罪的性犯罪者。雖然他現在已經自由，但代價卻很高。」<br />\n<br />\n原定入獄6年的阿當莊臣，於服判一半後便提前獲釋，雖然有傳他將會爭取到中超、中東地區落班，不過便被禁止單獨見其女兒。較早前，其前女友Stacey Flounders的身邊人士爆料，Stacey拒絕與阿當莊臣復合，任何接觸都只是為了他們4歲的女兒。<br />\n<br />\n他被控在2014至2015年間和15歲少女性交，更因此被新特蘭解約，而他於2016年3月被定罪前，曾與Stacey共同擁有一間價值180萬鎊的房屋。莊臣為出獄後生活所購買的200萬鎊新屋亦於早前爆光，有7間睡房、游泳池和保齡球館。"},{"pid":"b1aa29f4cfbb788a9d8000bafb5b04821f554a86","tid":1073203,"uid":11270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:49:20.000Z","msg":"11哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac043e58e8f1558aabb1f4939cc513fb87eb615e","tid":1073203,"uid":4826,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:50:16.000Z","msg":"叫湯大狀以過來人身分輔導下佢"},{"pid":"7be294b65a5b85cd7228ace9237eb77a3d50075b","tid":1073203,"uid":202348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T13:52:40.000Z","msg":"中東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBacha bazi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"310533abb7fd901ad995c0daa4e1a13d64cc8ec6","tid":1073203,"uid":37827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:10:34.000Z","msg":"淚灑貝克街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07694edd865d6273fcd7bceb244b2fe1fe2f6aef","tid":1073203,"uid":2040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"310533abb7fd901ad995c0daa4e1a13d64cc8ec6","tid":1073203,"uid":37827,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:10:34.000Z","msg":"淚灑貝克街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-22T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}